reviewText: thiz iz tha worst training video i have ever seen n my life... i can learn more by reading a book on automotive electronics... thiz guy sounds slow and retarded.

Part 1 received a lot of bad reviews. If you listen to their videos on youtube it's easy to see their systems are likely a scam. Video 1 - elect. diag. is poor, so how did this one receive just a single 5 start review with just a one word description? That was likely provided by someone affiliated with the company that makes these videos.
